| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0209 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1d607e44-b3d1-56a5-a0a7-5713ed4967fc"
